title: Ted Cruz says Donald Trump won't be Republican nominee
text: Sen. Ted Cruz said Thursday that he doesn't think that Donald Trump will capture the 2016 GOP presidential nomination and predicted that it is only a matter of time before most of the New York billionaire's supporters will move into his camp.
